snippet: Serena Williams' break from tennis at the end of last year to "just chill" appeared to have done her a world of good as the rejuvenated American bulldozed her way into the Australian Open final on Thursday....
lead_paragraph: Serena Williams' break from tennis at the end of last year to "just chill" appeared to have done her a world of good as the rejuvenated American bulldozed her way into the Australian Open final on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Serena Demolishes Radwanska to Make Final in Australia
headline.main: Serena Demolishes Radwanska to Make Final in Australia
